{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About Battle Wizard Attack</h2>Unleash the arcane power of eight legendary wizards in this action-packed pixel-art action RPG. Battle hordes of evil, master devastating spells, and leave a trail of pixelated destruction in your wake!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Non-Stop Action</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Dive straight into the fray! No grinding through skill trees or endless dialogue.<br></li><li> Customize your wizard between missions, then focus on pure, unadulterated action!<br></li><li> Obliterate massive, destructible environments as you battle across sprawling maps.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2621160/extras/Steam_BWA_Image_01.jpg?t=1736527723\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Wield the Power of 8 Legendary Wizards</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Storm Wizard: Command the elements with lightning and water-based spells.<br></li><li> Fire Warlock: Engulf your enemies in blazing infernos.<br></li><li> Ice Mage: Freeze foes in their tracks and conjure chilling attacks.<br></li><li> Earth Druid: Control the earth, shaping it to your will.<br></li><li> Blood Priest: Harness the power of blood magic for powerful attacks.<br></li><li> Ether Bender: Manipulate the fabric of reality with arcane spells.<br></li><li> Rainbow Channelist: Channel the power of the spectrum, unleashing beams of light.<br></li><li> Doom Witch: Curse your enemies and summon dark forces.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A World Steeped in German Folklore</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Encounter iconic creatures and legends from German mythology.<br></li><li> Battle through enchanted forests, haunted castles, and eerie villages.<br></li><li> Discover hidden lore and unravel the secrets of a land steeped in ancient magic.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Defeat Boss I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2621160/d0aa81c93a89537b045f05af78ef34344